	"subclassFeature": [
		{
			"name": "Circle of the Seasons",
			"source": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Seasons",
			"subclassSource": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"level": 2,
			"entries": [
				"在炎热的夏季激情之后，紧随其后的是凋零的秋天，很快就会迎来难以捉摸的冬季喘息，只为在春天重新绽放生命。于是这个过程不断重复，一次又一次。",
				"季节之环德鲁伊(revere this constant cycle)崇敬这个永恒的循环，借助大地的无数阶段来赋予他们的魔法以类似的多变性，并适应手头的任何情况。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Call Summer, Autumn, Winter, Spring|Druid|PHB|Seasons|CircleOfTheSeasons|2"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Call Summer, Autumn, Winter, Spring",
			"source": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Seasons",
			"subclassSource": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"level": 2,
			"header": 1,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 2nd-level Circle of the Seasons feature}",
				"作为一个动作，你可以消耗你的野性变身特性的使用次数，通过自己召唤一个季节的本质，暂时利用它的力量。",
				"召唤一个季节将使你可以在下面的季节法术表中获得对应的法术，以及你可以选择一个额外的德鲁伊零级法术。这些法术的施法能力为感知。",
				"这种变身持续8小时。如果你解除它（无需动作）、达到{@condition incapacitated}、死亡或再次使用这个特性，它会提前结束。",
				{
					"type": "table",
					"caption": "Seasonal Spells",
					"colLabels": [
						"Druid Level",
						"Summer's Assault",
						"Autumn's Decline",
						"Winter's Protection",
						"Spring's Resurgence"
					],
					"colStyles": [
						"col-2 text-center",
						"col-2.5",
						"col-2.5",
						"col-2.5",
						"col-2.5"
					],
					"rows": [
						[
							"2nd",
							"{@spell fire bolt}, {@spell magic missile}",
							"{@spell bane}, {@spell mind sliver|tce}",
							"{@spell ray of frost}, {@spell shield}",
							"{@spell bless}, {@spell minor illusion}"
						],
						[
							"3rd",
							"{@spell scorching ray}",
							"{@spell blindness/deafness}",
							"{@spell invisibility}",
							"{@spell aid}"
						],
						[
							"5th",
							"{@spell fireball}",
							"{@spell slow}",
							"{@spell fear}",
							"{@spell thunder step|xge}"
						],
						[
							"7th",
							"{@spell sickening radiance|xge}",
							"{@spell compulsion}",
							"{@spell otiluke's resilient sphere}",
							"{@spell death ward}"
						],
						[
							"9th",
							"{@spell dawn|xge}",
							"{@spell synaptic static|xge}",
							"{@spell wall of force}",
							"{@spell holy weapon|xge}"
						]
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Blessings of the Cycle",
			"source": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Seasons",
			"subclassSource": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"level": 6,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 6th-level Circle of the Seasons feature}",
				"你接纳了你所召唤的季节的另一个特质，使你在变身时获得特殊的恩惠：",
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Summer's Assault",
					"entries": [
						"每当你使用你的法术造成伤害时，你可以将你的熟练加值加到伤害结果中。"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Autumn's Decline",
					"entries": [
						"每当一个生物对你的法术的豁免检定失败时，你可以使其在其下一个回合结束前被你所{@condition charmed}。"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Winter's Protection",
					"entries": [
						"你在体质豁免检定上获得熟练加值，如果你已经熟练，那么在体质豁免检定上得到+2加值。"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Spring's Resurgence",
					"entries": [
						"每当你施放1级或更高级别的法术时，你可以使你选择的一个生物在你身边30英尺内获得临时生命值，数值等同于你的熟练加法术等级。如果它的生命值为0，它还会恢复1点生命值。"
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Call Solstice, Call Equinox",
			"source": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Seasons",
			"subclassSource": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"level": 10,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 10th-level Circle of the Seasons feature}",
				"你可以扩展你的野性变身特性的两次使用，同时召唤两个季节，利用它们交替的边界来融合它们各自的力量。这两个季节必须是相邻的 - 你不能同时召唤夏季和冬季，或秋季和春季。"
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Hidden Star in Four Seasons",
			"source": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Seasons",
			"subclassSource": "CircleOfTheSeasons",
			"level": 14,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 14th-level Circle of the Seasons feature}",
				"借助于季节之力，你可以轻松地召唤它们，作为一个奖励动作。此外，每次你使用野性变身来召唤时，你可以施放一个你可用的季节法术中的三级或更低级法术，而不消耗法术位。"
			]
		}
	]
